data.description: Welcome home to your charming one-story townhouse nestled in a peaceful neighborhood, offering a perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Step into the heart of the meticulously maintained home and discover the newly renovated kitchen, boasting modern finishes and ample cabinet space- ideal for culinary enthusiasts and social gatherings alike. Two cozy bedrooms and a beautifully updated bathroom, ensure a relaxing retreat for you and your family. Outside, a fully fenced yard provides a private oasis for outdoor relaxation and entertaining. Whether you're sipping your morning coffee on the patio or hosting a barbecue with friends, this serene setting offers endless possibilities for enjoyment and recreation. Enhanced by fresh light fixtures outside, the exterior exudes a warm ambiance, inviting you to unwind under the starlit sky. Water filtration system conveys with the home. Experience the ease of townhouse living with all the modern comforts you desire.
